---
import "../styles/Menu.css";
---

<section class="section menu" aria-label="menu-label" id="menu">
        <div class="container">
          <p class="section-subtitle text-center label-2">Pronta Entrega</p>

          <h2 class="headline-1 section-title text-center">
            Confira Nossos Itens Disponíveis
          </h2>

          <ul class="grid-list">
            <li>
              <div class="menu-card hover:card">
                <figure
                  class="card-banner img-holder"
                  style="--width: 100; --height: 100;"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/images/menu-1.png"
                    width="100"
                    height="100"
                    loading="lazy"
                    alt="Greek Salad"
                    class="img-cover"
                  />
                </figure>

                <div>
                  <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="title-3">
                      <a href="#" class="card-title"
                        >Drone - Rainbow Six Siege</a
                      >
                    </h3>

                    <span class="badge label-1">New</span>

                    <span class="span title-2">R$150,00</span>
                  </div>

                  <p class="card-text label-1">
                    Seu melhor amigo na espionagem, permitindo explorar, marcar
                    inimigos e planejar estratégias sem ser detectado.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="menu-card hover:card">
                <figure
                  class="card-banner img-holder"
                  style="--width: 100; --height: 100;"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/images/menu-2.png"
                    width="100"
                    height="100"
                    loading="lazy"
                    alt="Lasagne"
                    class="img-cover"
                  />
                </figure>

                <div>
                  <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="title-3">
                      <a href="#" class="card-title"
                        >Figures Hollow Knight - Individual</a
                      >
                    </h3>

                    <span class="span title-2">R$50,00</span>
                  </div>

                  <p class="card-text label-1">
                    O Cavaleiro do Vazio mais amado do mundo e a misteriosa
                    princesa-protetora das ruínas de Hallownest.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="menu-card hover:card">
                <figure
                  class="card-banner img-holder"
                  style="--width: 100; --height: 100;"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/images/menu-3.png"
                    width="100"
                    height="100"
                    loading="lazy"
                    alt="Butternut Pumpkin"
                    class="img-cover"
                  />
                </figure>

                <div>
                  <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="title-3">
                      <a href="#" class="card-title">Busto Gollum</a>
                    </h3>

                    <span class="badge label-1">New</span>

                    <span class="span title-2">R$120,00</span>
                  </div>

                  <p class="card-text label-1">
                    Criatura intrigante e complexa, cuja lealdade oscila entre a
                    luz e a escuridão, mantendo-nos cativados com sua dualidade.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="menu-card hover:card">
                <figure
                  class="card-banner img-holder"
                  style="--width: 100; --height: 100;"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/images/menu-4.png"
                    width="100"
                    height="100"
                    loading="lazy"
                    alt="Tokusen Wagyu"
                    class="img-cover"
                  />
                </figure>

                <div>
                  <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="title-3">
                      <a href="#" class="card-title">Trono de Ferro - GOT</a>
                    </h3>

                    <span class="badge label-1">New</span>

                    <span class="span title-2">R$80,00</span>
                  </div>

                  <p class="card-text label-1">
                    No jogo dos tronos, apenas um se assenta no Trono de Ferro.
                    Será você capaz aquele de conquistar o poder?
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="menu-card hover:card">
                <figure
                  class="card-banner img-holder"
                  style="--width: 100; --height: 100;"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/images/menu-5.png"
                    width="100"
                    height="100"
                    loading="lazy"
                    alt="Olivas Rellenas"
                    class="img-cover"
                  />
                </figure>

                <div>
                  <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="title-3">
                      <a href="#" class="card-title"
                        >Keycaps Valorant - Unitário</a
                      >
                    </h3>

                    <span class="span title-2">R$25,00</span>
                  </div>

                  <p class="card-text label-1">
                    Seu teclado com um visual único que reflete sua paixão pelo
                    jogo e garante uma jogabilidade ainda mais imersiva.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>

            <li>
              <div class="menu-card hover:card">
                <figure
                  class="card-banner img-holder"
                  style="--width: 100; --height: 100;"
                >
                  <img
                    src="/assets/images/menu-6.png"
                    width="100"
                    height="100"
                    loading="lazy"
                    alt="Opu Fish"
                    class="img-cover"
                  />
                </figure>

                <div>
                  <div class="title-wrapper">
                    <h3 class="title-3">
                      <a href="#" class="card-title">Logo F1</a>
                    </h3>

                    <span class="span title-2">R$100,00</span>
                  </div>

                  <p class="card-text label-1">
                    Transforme sua casa em uma pista de corrida com o icônico
                    logo da Fórmula 1.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <p class="menu-text text-center">
            Encomendas personalizadas via <span class="span">Instagram</span> ou
            <span class="span">E-mail</span>.
          </p>

          <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">
            <span class="text text-1">Contato</span>

            <span class="text text-2" aria-hidden="true">Contato</span>
          </a>

          <img
            src="/assets/images/shape-5.png"
            width="921"
            height="1036"
            loading="lazy"
            alt="shape"
            class="shape shape-2 move-anim"
          />
          <img
            src="/assets/images/shape-6.png"
            width="343"
            height="345"
            loading="lazy"
            alt="shape"
            class="shape shape-3 move-anim"
          />
        </div>
      </section>